::GoldenEye/Battera/Feline::

GoldenEye:
She smiled and hugged Dollen. "We made it out alive at least." she 
kissed Dollen on the cheek and smiled at him. "Are you alright?"

Battera::
She got Vulois transmission and sighed in relief. "Thank the Matrix 
you are alright.  I have talked tot he maximal leader here at the 
Cybertron Fire and she has agreed to come to the talks. What is going 
on now?  Are we still having hte talks in the old Embassy?  
Cybershark left from here and I do not know where he is.  What will 
you have me do now?  Leave the coordnants tot he embassy and go try 
to talk to another leader or stay here and guide the maximal leader 
to you?"

Feline:
She walked out of the CR lab and down the hall.  She swayed her hips 
and twitched her tail as she walked.  She went into the mess hall and 
saw two other bots there.  She smiled at them and went to a food 
dispencer.  She got something to eat and sat down at a corner table, 
away from the other bots.  She acted shy around them and didn't make 
eye contact after she sat down.
